simulator.elevatorcontrol

Class MessageDictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulator.elevatorcontrol.MessageDictionary

  • public class MessageDictionary
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines constants for CAN IDs that are used throughout the simulator. The default values will work for early projects. Later on, you will modify these values when you create a network schedule.
